recommendation_prompt:
Write a 2-sentence hiring recommendation for this candidate:

Candidate: {candidate.name} | Role: {candidate.current_role} | Exp: {candidate.years_of_experience}y
Overall Score: {score.overall_score}/100 | Skill Match: {score.skill_match_score}%
Matched Skills: {matched_skills} 
Missing Skills: {missing_skills}
Job Title: {jd.title} | Required Skills: {required_skills}

Write exactly 2 sentences: first on their strengths, second on gaps/concerns or why to proceed.
Be specific, objective, and concise. No preamble.
